~ start
Guide: Hey there, traveler! Heading into the desert gauntlet?
Guide: Let me tell you how it works before you go.
Guide: Press [ I ] to jump over obstacles in your path.
Guide: Press [ K ] to crouch under low-hanging hazards.
Guide: Keep your eyes open for shiny Gems scattered along the route.
Guide: Collect them — you can spend those Gems at the shop later!
Guide: Some obstacles can be destroyed on the spot.
Guide: If you have a Recharge item, click on the obstacle to blast it apart.
Guide: Good luck out there. You'll need it!
=> END
